SUMMER VENGEANCE MATCH UP: QUARTER FINALS!
DIA ZERVA
The Iron Maiden
HT: 5'5
WT: 135lbs
Season record (4-0)
Lifetime record (5-1)
Ranked 1st
WENONA
The Gymnast
HT: 5'8
WT: 120lbs
Season record (1-1)
Lifetime record (7-6)
Ranked 8th
Welcome to the 2009 Championship tournament. The top 16 wrestlers of the season face off in a single elimination tournament. Check out the Summer Vengeance Bracket here.
Dia Zerva was last years runner up to the Championship. This year she is ranked 1st and is undefeated. Few wrestlers train off the mat as hard as Dia and it shows.
Wenona is a seasoned veteran, the most ripped warrior we have. A former All-American Gymnast, this girl brings the muscle and the flexibility. Wenona is in the best shape of her wrestling career and has been one of the most active wrestlers this year if you add in the Tag Team league
Amazing competition in this match up. Both girls giving all they have. However there is a reason Dia is ranked 1st and she shows you why! It was a great season for Wenona but it ends today with a brutal ass fucking for losing.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE TOURNAMENT MATCH UP!
